===Etymology===
Cognate with {{och-l|喬|tall; lofty}}, {{och-l|憍|id=1|to lift the head}}, {{och-l|撟|id=2|to lift}}, and {{och-l|嶠|peak}}. Beyond these, {{och-l|高|high; tall}} and {{och-l|蹻|id=1|martial; vigorous}} could be allofams ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}).

